        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2019-07-26 17:53:57.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 6:\n\n> I overlooked this during the review - still need to copy these\n > params into the Properties object.\n\nthe one caveat is the \"managed\" property.  It defaults to \"true\", which is not the gson default.  Options I can think of:\n1) don't copy it for now; this should work for all of our current cases\n2) add a custom gson adapter to set it to true if not specified\n3) use Boolean instead of boolean in BusParams; then ParamUtils would only copy it if it's non-null (assumes gson leaves Boolean as null if not specified in the json)",
        "patchset_number": 6
      }
    ]
  }
